## Limitations

This report is based on available data and studies up to October 2023. The effectiveness of online versus classroom learning can vary significantly depending on factors such as the subject matter, the quality of the online platform, and the individual learning styles of students. Additionally, the rapid evolution of technology and educational methodologies means that findings may change as new research emerges. Further studies are needed to explore long-term outcomes and the impact of hybrid learning models.